APPENDIX A: How to attribute OpenFreight by Freightos

The Standards will already contain appropriate attribution. Do not delete this attribution when creating Derivative Works.

Data should always reference the Standard for example
<?xml version="1.0"?> 
<xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://OpenFreight.org/standardURL"> 
<myDoc…>
or
<?xml version="1.0"?> 
<xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://me.com/derivativeWorkStandardURL"> 
<!--derivativeWorkStandardURL is a derivative of  
http://OpenFreight.org/standardURL-->
<myDoc…>



